---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "Amino Blend | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "A mix of amino acids to support performance and recovery.", "canonical": "/services/vitamin-injections/amino-blend", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>

<section class="relative isolate bg-white text-neutral-900">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-24">
    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-4">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-neutral-700">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-1">/</span>
      <a href="/services" class="hover:text-neutral-700">Services</a>
      <span class="mx-1">/</span>
      <span class="text-neutral-800">Amino Blend</span>
    </nav>

    <!-- Title + Subtitle -->
    <header class="mb-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Amino Blend</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-neutral-700">A mix of amino acids to support performance and recovery.</p>
    </header>

    <hr class="my-10 border-neutral-200">

    <!-- 1) Description -->
    <section aria-label="Description" class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Description</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-700">
        This service is designed to provide refined, natural‑looking improvements with an emphasis on comfort and safety.
        We tailor technique and approach to your goals, explain each step, and set clear expectations for outcomes and maintenance.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-700">
        During a brief consultation, we map your features and review your medical history to determine candidacy and customize the plan.
        The intent is a polished, balanced result rather than an overdone look.
      </p>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-10 border-neutral-200">

    <!-- 2) Benefits -->
    <section aria-label="Benefits" class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Benefits</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-700">Key advantages may include:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-neutral-700">
        <li>Personalized approach aligned with your anatomy and goals</li>
        <li>Modern techniques for comfort and natural‑looking outcomes</li>
        <li>Clear, concise aftercare to support a smooth recovery</li>
        <li>Quality products/devices and trained providers</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-10 border-neutral-200">

    <!-- 3) How It Works -->
    <section aria-label="How It Works" class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">How It Works</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-700">
        We match technique, dosing, or device settings to the indication and area being addressed. The plan accounts for your timeline,
        tolerance, and preferences. We also discuss what complements or alternatives might better suit adjacent concerns.
      </p>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-10 border-neutral-200">

    <!-- 4) The Process -->
    <section aria-label="The Process" class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">The Process</h2>
      <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
        <li><span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Consultation</span> — goal setting, medical history, candidacy, and mapping.</li>
        <li><span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Treatment</span> — technique tailored to the indication and area.</li>
        <li><span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Review & Next Steps</span> — what to expect, check‑ins, and maintenance when helpful.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-10 border-neutral-200">

    <!-- 5) Pre and Post-Treatment Instructions -->
    <section aria-label="Pre and Post‑Treatment Instructions" class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Pre and Post‑Treatment Instructions</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-700">
        You’ll receive a concise handout adapted to your service. In general, arrive with clean skin, avoid irritants when advised,
        and follow the simple do’s and don’ts provided after your session.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Before your visit</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-neutral-700">
            <li>Avoid new actives or irritants as directed</li>
            <li>Disclose medications, allergies, and procedures</li>
            <li>Hydrate and come with clean skin</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-neutral-900">After your visit</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-neutral-700">
            <li>Follow your specific post‑care steps</li>
            <li>Protect the area from heat/sun and avoid harsh actives</li>
            <li>Reach out with any unexpected reactions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-10 border-neutral-200">

    <!-- 6) Frequently Asked Questions -->
    <section aria-label="Frequently Asked Questions" class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <details class="group rounded-md border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
        <summary class="font-medium text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer">How many sessions will I need?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-700">It depends on the indication, area, and your goals. Your provider will outline a plan that covers initial and maintenance visits if appropriate.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="group rounded-md border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
        <summary class="font-medium text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer">Will it look natural?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-700">Our approach emphasizes harmony, proportion, and a refined finish tailored to your features.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="group rounded-md border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
        <summary class="font-medium text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer">Is there downtime?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-700">Most services have minimal downtime; we review specifics for your situation and provide easy post‑care guidelines.</p>
      </details>
      <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm">*Informational content only; not medical advice. Individual results vary.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
